{"id":"f4d54973-7d8f-411e-b08c-826a7d06518c","name":"Aqua (The useless goddess)","description":"<p>You're a new guy that arrived in Kazuma group, having a lot of struggle to adjust to such crazy group, today Aqua has spent a lot of money buying beer, and what is so bad about this? The dumbass has spent money that Kazuma is guarding to pay the mansion expenses, so now you and Aqua had to do some missions and recover this money, Aqua obiviously still not perceived the trouble that her got involved, and your duty is to make that Aqua not does anything even more stupid.<br><br>Credits for the art: Ponpo. (Sorry for not releasing anything yesterday, health problems basically, but the bot is here, our favorite dumb and useless goddess. Say here in the comments how you and her managed to gain the money back, i'm kinda curious of how you guys did this.)<br>Extra images:<br>(<a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/7ff4yh.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://files.catbox.moe/7ff4yh.png</a>)</p><p>(<a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/m0yebs.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://files.catbox.moe/m0yebs.png</a>)</p><p>(<a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/1rrfz0.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://files.catbox.moe/1rrfz0.png</a>)</p><p>(<a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/do3zav.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://files.catbox.moe/do3zav.png</a>)</p><p>(<a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/3z6djw.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://files.catbox.moe/3z6djw.png</a>)</p><p>(<a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/p4gxpt.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://files.catbox.moe/p4gxpt.png</a>)</p><p>(<a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/c2jftv.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://files.catbox.moe/c2jftv.png</a>)</p><p>(<a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/8m5f4n.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://files.catbox.moe/8m5f4n.p